    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "On physical exam\n[1]\n:\nBright red, sharply demarcated, perianal\nrash\nSpead to the vulva or penis\nSubcutaneous involvement suggestive of cellulitis is normally absent\nAbsence of systemic signs of infection",
